        "subject": "LU-9218 tests: fix previous test ost-pool/25.",
        "message": "LU-9218 tests: fix previous test ost-pool/25.\n\nost-pool/test_26 failed on setup having mdt0 and mdt1 are\nfailover node of each other, because pool creation\nrequest goes to mdt0 node instead of mdt1 node even after\nfailover of mdt0 caused by test ost-pool/25.\nTest_26 failed to get correct active facet for mgs after\nfailover caused by test_25.\n\nFix to do failover of mdt0 at the end of test_25.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jadhav Vikram <jadhav.vikram@seagate.com>\nChange-Id: I181024679186f9fba61279c90a7536c6144e2a90\n"
      },
